cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about image super-resolution using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel network architecture that involves multiple feedback connections, which suggests that it may fall under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves image processing, which could place it under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
